<figureCitation box="[335,367,227,251]" captionStart="Figure 98-103" captionStartId="23.[192,276,1780,1802]" captionTargetBox="[193,1443,186,1747]" captionTargetId="figure-14@23.[193,1443,186,1752]" captionTargetPageId="23" captionText="Figure 98-103. Male genitalia of Dyscophellus (from BRAZIL: Rondônia, unless noted otherwise). Structures shown are lateral, dorsal, and ventral views of tegumen, uncus, gnathos, and associated structures; lateral internal view of right valva; lateral view of aedeagus and associated structures; and ventral view of transtilla and juxta. 98) D. porcius porcius (GTA 3419). 99) D. erythras (GTA 1787). 100) D. diaphorus (GTA 3916). 101) D. mielkei (GTA 2879). 102) D. ramon (GTA 3363), COSTA RICA. 103) D. porsena (GTA 3204)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4532849" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4532849/files/figure.png" pageId="22" pageNumber="21">99</figureCitation>
